  <brief_title>Alglucosidase Alfa Pompe Safety Sub-Registry</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Safety Sub-Registry to Assess Anaphylaxis and Severe Allergic Reactions, and Severe Cutaneous and Systemic Immune Complex Mediated Reactions With Alglucosidase Alfa Treatment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Genzyme, a Sanofi Company</agency>
